# A2: reason=offline in the RESULT line (engine rc=0 but the server was unreachable mid-run)
# must render as an unreachable-server message — the pre-A2 0/0 glob said "Save already in
# sync" while tailscaled was down (2026-07-02 Smart Pro field lie).
desc Game Manager: sync-save reason=offline -> honest unreachable message, never "in sync"
config paired
seeded
sdfile+ Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda.gba
pick 0|Game Manager
pick 0|Game Boy Advance (GBA)
pick 0|✓ Zelda.gba
pick 0|Sync save now
pick 2|
engine 0|RESULT pulled=0 pushed=0 ghosts=0 reason=offline
expect_exit 0
expect_trace ENGINE --sync-save
expect_log err: Couldn't reach your server - check the server or your connection, then retry
